<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <style>
    span {
      color: #6ebf4a;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      img {
        height: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <div
      style="
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #4b5563;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      "
    >
      <div class="container" style="background-color: white; padding: 20px">
        <a href="https://www.kwanza.io" target="_blank">
          <img
            style="height: 35px"
            src="https://api.kwanza.io/files/kwanza.png"
          />
        </a>

        <div id="heading">
          <h1 style="color: #222d38">Contract Submitted Successfully</h1>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px">Hi <%- name %></p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px">
          Weâ€™re pleased to inform you that your contract has been successfully
          signed. Thank you for completing this step. You can download a copy of
          the signed contract by pressing the button below. If any further
          details are needed, our team will reach out to you.
        </p>

        <button
          style="
            background-color: #6ebf4a;
            padding: 12px 40px;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
          "
        >
          <a style="color: white; text-decoration: none" href="<%- pdfUrl %>"
            >Download Contract</a
          >
        </button>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af">
        <p>
          This email was sent to <span><%- email %></span>. If you'd rather not
          receive this kind of email, you can <span>unsubscribe</span> or
          <span>manage your email preferences.</span>
        </p>
        <p>House No 346 Senga RD, Mikocheni, Dar es salaam</p>

        <table
          width="100%"
          cellpadding="0"
          cellspacing="0"
          style="width: 100%; table-layout: fixed"
        >
          <tr>
            <!-- Logo -->
            <td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; padding: 0">
              <img
                src="https://api.kwanza.io/files/k.png"
                alt="Kwanza Logo"
                style="height: 30px; display: block"
              />
            </td>

            <!-- Social Icons -->
            <td style="text-align: right; vertical-align: middle; padding: 0">
              <a
                href="https://x.com/kwanzanetwork?lang=en"
                target="_blank"
                style="text-decoration: none"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://api.kwanza.io/files/twitter.png"
                  alt="Twitter"
                  style="height: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px"
                />
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/kwanza-digital-network/?viewAsMember=true"
                target="_blank"
                style="text-decoration: none"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://api.kwanza.io/files/linkedin.png"
                  alt="LinkedIn"
                  style="height: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px"
                />
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/kwanzadesk/"
                target="_blank"
                style="text-decoration: none"
              >
                <img
                  src="https://api.kwanza.io/files/insta.png"
                  alt="Instagram"
                  style="height: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-left: 10px"
                />
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
